00:04:07.711 --> 00:04:09.360
It's fine. You don't have to thank me.

00:04:10.919 --> 00:04:13.919
I heard you studied overseas
since you were young?

00:04:13.919 --> 00:04:14.599
Yes.

00:04:15.199 --> 00:04:16.920
