He said the project might fall through.

00:04:39.560 --> 00:04:40.560
Mr. Jing?

00:04:41.560 --> 00:04:42.360
Hello?

00:04:46.360 --> 00:04:48.000
I thought we had a deal.

00:04:48.022 --> 00:04:49.800
