10,000 carats of diamonds,

00:04:49.800 --> 00:04:51.920
we'll lose half our orders this quarter.

00:04:52.120 --> 00:04:53.800
The mine is in a war zone right now.

00:04:53.800 --> 00:04:55.319
This matter is out of our hands.

00:04:55.360 --> 00:04:57.399
But I already signed the contract.

00:04:58.199 --> 00:04:59.319
We'll have to sign a new one.

00:05:00.160 --> 00:05:00.920
All right.

00:05:00.920 --> 00:05:01.920
Do you have time tonight?

00:05:01.920 --> 00:05:03.000
