00:05:14.950 --> 00:05:16.244
before coming into my office?

00:05:17.560 --> 00:05:18.560
Sorry.

00:05:19.199 --> 00:05:20.120
Don't be mad.

00:05:20.120 --> 00:05:21.509
Frowning gives you wrinkles,

00:05:21.510 --> 00:05:22.822
and it'll ruin your pretty face.

00:05:23.680 --> 00:05:24.480
Here's your coffee.

00:05:31.279 --> 00:05:32.279
Get to work.

00:05:38.360 --> 00:05:40.319
Did she wake up
on the wrong side of the bed?

00:05:40.920 --> 00:05:42.319
Don't go in. Don't provoke her.

00:05:43.319 --> 00:05:44.199
This should do it.

00:05:51.920 --> 00:05:52.879
Ms. Gu is busy.

00:05:54.920 --> 00:05:55.879
Mr. Xingchen.

00:05:57.720 --> 00:05:58.759
How's work?

00:06:01.511 --> 00:06:02.630
I need to speak with Ms. Gu.

00:06:03.759 --> 00:06:04.560
Hold up.

00:06:06.120 --> 00:06:07.319
I need to make a call.

00:06:19.279 --> 00:06:20.360
What is it now?

00:06:20.759 --> 00:06:23.040
Someone unrelated
to our company is here asking for you.

00:06:23.040 --> 00:06:24.160
Do you want to meet him?

00:06:24.199 --> 00:06:25.560
You're only a few steps away.

00:06:26.000 --> 00:06:27.680
Was a phone call necessary?

00:06:27.680 --> 00:06:28.822
If you don't, I'll send...

00:06:34.879 --> 00:06:36.160
Mo Li, you're here.

00:06:36.560 --> 00:06:37.399
Ms. Liusu.

00:06:38.199 --> 00:06:40.560
Perfect timing. I wanted to talk to you

00:06:40.560 --> 00:06:42.480
about the charity auction.

00:06:42.680 --> 00:06:44.759
I'd like to set up a small stage

00:06:44.759 --> 00:06:47.279
to display the kids' drawings.

00:06:47.759 --> 00:06:50.399
And we need a backdrop

00:06:50.399 --> 00:06:51.920
for the media and guests

00:06:51.920 --> 00:06:53.319
to take photos.

00:06:54.040 --> 00:06:55.759
Actually, this whole auction

00:06:56.160 --> 00:06:58.519
is an opportunity
Ms. Baozhu arranged for me.

00:06:58.920 --> 00:07:00.480
I feel a little uncomfortable

00:07:00.480 --> 00:07:01.839
about that.

00:07:03.800 --> 00:07:04.680
Look.

00:07:05.560 --> 00:07:06.839
Are those two

00:07:07.160 --> 00:07:08.720
standing too close?

00:07:08.920 --> 00:07:10.000
No.

00:07:10.160 --> 00:07:12.639
Since when has Ms. Gu
been that close with anyone?

00:07:14.244 --> 00:07:15.422
He's trying to take advantage.

00:07:15.466 --> 00:07:16.555
He's just here to hit on her.

00:07:16.577 --> 00:07:17.480
No.

00:07:17.600 --> 00:07:18.755
You're too sensitive.

00:07:19.399 --> 00:07:21.759
Xinghan has been supporting
the orphanage for years.

00:07:21.759 --> 00:07:23.879
Just treat this as work.

00:07:24.160 --> 00:07:24.600
It's not...

00:07:25.759 --> 00:07:26.680
Ms. Liusu.

00:07:27.000 --> 00:07:28.319
Are you free this Saturday?

00:07:28.688 --> 00:07:30.390
Would you like to watch a play together?

00:07:35.680 --> 00:07:36.759
I'm sorry, Mo Li.

00:07:36.759 --> 00:07:38.360
I'm a bit swamped this week.

00:07:39.120 --> 00:07:40.160
Is something wrong

00:07:40.480 --> 00:07:41.560
at GL?

00:07:43.040 --> 00:07:44.560
Are you planning to jump ship to GL?

00:07:44.560 --> 00:07:45.920
Why do you care so much about GL?

00:07:47.600 --> 00:07:49.319
We're just checking in on each other.

00:07:49.920 --> 00:07:51.279
What are you, a saint?

00:07:51.519 --> 00:07:53.160
Telling you won't solve anything.

00:07:53.800 --> 00:07:56.279
Are you speaking to me as Mr. Xingchen

00:07:56.279 --> 00:07:57.079
right now

00:07:58.199 --> 00:07:59.920
or as Secretary Lu?

00:08:00.879 --> 00:08:01.800
I...

00:08:02.160 --> 00:08:03.120
Lu Xingchen.

00:08:05.920 --> 00:08:07.519
Sorry about this, Mo Li.

00:08:07.680 --> 00:08:10.079
This does concern trade secrets.

00:08:10.120 --> 00:08:11.759
You have plenty on your plate as it is.

00:08:11.759 --> 00:08:13.959
Don't worry about us.
We've troubled you enough...

00:08:13.959 --> 00:08:14.879
Gu Liusu!

00:08:15.480 --> 00:08:16.959
I'm the one who's been helping you.

00:08:16.959 --> 00:08:18.879
Why do you always take his side?

00:08:18.879 --> 00:08:21.399
Lu Xingchen, if you want to argue,
do it somewhere else.

00:08:38.360 --> 00:08:40.080
Mr. Xingchen is such a handful.

00:08:40.080 --> 00:08:42.960
I don't know if I should apologize
to you or if you should apologize to me.

00:08:42.960 --> 00:08:43.679
It's fine.

00:08:44.039 --> 00:08:45.000
I'll apologize.

00:08:45.519 --> 00:08:47.879
I should get back
to work on the charity auction.

00:08:49.320 --> 00:08:50.960
I'll reach out again when you have time.

00:08:53.720 --> 00:08:54.679
I'll take my leave.

00:08:55.559 --> 00:08:56.360
Goodbye.

